# Merge Databases

Merge a MSSQL database on a Cisco VPN into an Oracle database on a Juniper VPN

## Install Dependencies

In order to merge databases, you should have the following installed in your PC.

#### 1. Windows 10 + Bash
How to install bash: https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/commandline/wsl/install_guide

#### 2. Install ruby (Recommended version: 2.3.1)
How to install ruby on Windows: http://rubyinstaller.org/

#### 3. Install FreeTDS
How to install FreeTDS on Windows: https://sourceforge.net/projects/freetdswindows/

#### 4. Install TinyTDS
To install, run the follwing command on terminal
```
gem install tiny_tds
```

## Add Local Info
You need to add your information anywhere in the code where it says ``` # ADD INFO! ```
Go through each file or do a dir search to find the comment.

## Usage

Run ``` rake ``` in the bash terminal. You must be in merge_databases (root) dir.
